class="t m66c x1e hf y84a ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The reply he received from his friend changed his life. He </div><div class="t m66d x1d hf y84b ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gathered his fellow workers around him to tell them what the Lord had </div><div class="t m66e x1d hf y84c ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">done for his soul. &quot;I looked to Jesus,&quot; he said, and &quot;Oh, how joy </div><div class="t m597 x1d hf y84d ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">flowed!&quot; Thus, other hearts were moved and blessed and &quot;rivers of </div><div class="t m66f x1d hf y84e ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">living water&quot; flowed forth that still flow today. </div><div class="t m9e x1e hf y1ed ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As you study this week&apos;s lesson, learn more about the reply Taylor </div><div class="t m132 x1d hf y84f ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">received and how it can transform your life. </div><div class="t m24d x1d h18 y850 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE WEEK AT A GLANCE: </div><div class="t mdb x50 h18 y30 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. </div><div class="t m654 x3e h18 y30 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sitting Down With Jesus (John 14:1). </div><div class="t m125 x61 h18 y851 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II. </div><div class="t m227 x9f h18 y851 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Future Is Now! (John 14:1-3). </div><div class="t m92 x1d h18 y852 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">III. </div><div class="t m11c x9f h18 y852 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No Real Separation (John 14:4-6; 15-23). </div><div class="t m129 x1d h18 y853 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IV. </div><div class="t m27d x9f h18 y59d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I Am the Vine; You Are the Branches&quot; (John 15:1-11, NIV). </div><div class="t m12b x61 h18 y264 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">V. </div><div class="t m3dd x9f h18 y264 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Bear Fruit (John 15:1-16). </div><div class="t m458 x1d h18 y1f6 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: &quot;Abide in Me and I in you. As the branch </div><div class="t m1da x1d h18 y1a5 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cannot bear fruit of itself, unless it abides in the vine, neither can </div><div class="t m3dd x1d h18 y854 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you, unless you abide in Me&quot; (John 15:4, NKJV). </div><div class="t m160 x1d h18 y268 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">*(Study </div><div class="t m485 x8 hf y268 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this week&apos;s lesson to prepare for Sabbath, March 10.) </div><div class="t m3dc x41 hf y855 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">80 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
